      <title>香港财经事务局局长谈香港资本市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/hk-secretary-for-financial-services-on-hk-capital-market-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港财经事务及库务局局长许志永讨论了政府如何看待香港的传统企业。他在亚洲金融论坛的间隙与 David Ingles 和 Rebecca Choong Wilkins 进行了交谈，主题是“与 Haslinda Amin 的见解”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/hk-secretary-for-financial-services-on-hk-capital-market-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 07:39:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>硫酸镍期货在新加坡首次亮相，以满足不断增长的需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/nickel-sulphate-futures-debut-in-singapore-to-tap-growing-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡 Abaxx 交易所推出了硫酸镍期货合约，以满足对电池成分日益增长的需求，并解决不同类型金属之间的价格差异。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/nickel-sulphate-futures-debut-in-singapore-to-tap-growing-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 07:36:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雷恩称无论美联储采取何种举措，欧洲央行都需要进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/more-ecb-rate-cuts-needed-irrespective-of-fed-moves-rehn-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员奥利·雷恩表示，无论美联储采取何种措施，欧洲央行都应继续降低借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/more-ecb-rate-cuts-needed-irrespective-of-fed-moves-rehn-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 07:33:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元上涨、油价飙升，卢比跌破 86 创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/rupee-falls-past-86-to-new-record-on-dollar-rally-oil-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国强劲的就业数据抑制了对美联储进一步降息的预期，且油价飙升影响了印度这个石油净进口国的信心，印度卢比兑美元跌破了86的关键心理水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/rupee-falls-past-86-to-new-record-on-dollar-rally-oil-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 04:57:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
